{"word":"G350 - ἀνακρίνω - anakrínō - an-ak-ree'-no - Ask","slug":"G350","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνακρίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>anakrínō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>an-ak-ree'-no"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ask"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03BD;&#x03B1;&#x03BA;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - anakrino&#x0304;</b> - <i>an-ak-ree'-no</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>; properly to <i>scrutinize</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>investigate</i>, <i>interrogate</i>, <i>determine:</i> - ask, question, discern, examine, judge, search."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843\">G843</a>, <a href=\"#/G87\">G87</a>"}]}